<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l4">graf <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Ötıng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mıt ıren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l5"><expan>leıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> ın <expan>Nördlıng<ex>er</ex></expan> markt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>belaıte<ex>n</ex></expan> well / darinn Jr <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l6">mıt den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu <expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ ſıe alle auf <expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>mıteınand<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ʒıehe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
